  <summary date="2019-12-30T14:11:51Z" status="Introduced in House">Burial Rights for America&#8217;s Veterans&#8217; Efforts Act of 2019 or the BRAVE Act of 2019

This bill increases the amounts payable through the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) for (1) burial and funeral expenses of veterans, and (2) such expenses in connection with a veteran's death due to a service-connected disability.

 The VA shall also increase such amounts each fiscal year to account for inflation.</summary>
